---
<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Got questions? We've got answers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-accordion glass-panel">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What exactly is spiritual stalking?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Spiritual stalking occurs when a person, group, or entity persistently attaches to your energy field without your consent. This can manifest as chronic exhaustion, sudden mood swings, feeling watched, or unexplainable streaks of "bad luck".</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Will these techniques work if I've never done energy work before?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Yes. The guide is designed to be highly approachable. We use practical, reproducible frameworks that do not require years of meditation or esoteric knowledge to apply successfully.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do I access the materials after purchase?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Immediately after checkout via Whop, you'll receive an email with your secure login details. You will have instant access to the PDF guide and the private community platform.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is there a money-back guarantee?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>We stand by our methods. If you actively apply the shielding techniques for 30 days and see no reduction in your symptoms, reach out to our support team for a full refund.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq-section {
    padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .faq-accordion {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0; /* Override glass-panel padding */
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }

  .faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  summary {
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--text-main);
    transition: background var(--transition-fast);
  }

  summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  summary::after {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    right: 2rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  details[open] summary {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
  }

  details[open] summary::after {
    content: '−';
  }

  .faq-content {
    padding: 0 2rem 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    animation: slideDown 0.3s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes slideDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .mb-12 { margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    summary { padding: 1.2rem 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    summary::after { right: 1rem; }
    .faq-content { padding: 0 1rem 1.2rem; }
  }
</style>
